column5: Thanks Glen...I think..... LOL  Yeah...I'm here far too much, but at least it's mostly at the office, where I have time to post.....  This board has given a lot to me (and Bly)...it makes participating very easy....we've met a lot of great people via this board.
One can only aspire..to perchance... capture a glimmer, a faint spark,...of Cliff's talent(s).
....Wow, I think the only thing to say Cliff is, get back to wrk!
awesome!  I always enjoy your posts and your insight into fishing!  Cheers!
Like I said Cliff,glad to have you here. Joe
